  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Cloud Engineer (AWS Focus)",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a Senior AWS Cloud Engineer to support the design, implementation, and operation of enterprise-scale AWS cloud environments. This role focuses on delivering secure, scalable cloud solutions within regulated and high-availability environments, working closely with cross-functional teams.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li>Design, implement, and operate AWS cloud infrastructure at scale.</li><li>Manage and secure core AWS services including compute, storage, networking, and identity.</li><li>Ensure cloud environments meet security, compliance, and operational standards.</li><li>Support cloud project delivery and operational handover.</li><li>Troubleshoot complex cloud issues and perform root cause analysis.</li><li>Implement automation and infrastructure-as-code where applicable.</li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li>Proven experience managing AWS environments at scale.</li><li>Strong hands-on knowledge of EC2, S3, VPC, Lambda, RDS, IAM, and CloudWatch.</li><li>Good understanding of AWS networking, security, and identity management.</li><li>Experience delivering cloud solutions in enterprise or regulated environments.</li><li>Strong problem-solving and communication skills.</li><li>AWS certifications are highly desirable.</li><li>Experience with IaC tools (CloudFormation, Terraform, Ansible) is an advantage.</li><li>Exposure to Docker and Kubernetes is a plus.</li></ul><p><strong>To Apply</strong><br />To apply or find out more information on this role, please email us or send in your updated resume to:<br /><a href=\"https://www.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/job/information-technology/cloud-security-engineer-star-career-consulting-ab89cb320ecde87bec0a37286f341b44#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lynn.tay@starcareerconsulting.com</a></p><p><strong>Lynn Tay</strong> (Reg. No. R1876711)<br /><strong>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD</strong> (EA Licence: 20C0353)</p>",
